In this file we prove that `real.log` is infinitely smooth at all nonzero `x : ‚Ñù`. We also prove
that the series `‚àë' n : ‚Ñï, x ^ (n + 1) / (n + 1)` converges to `(-real.log (1 - x))` for all
`x : ‚Ñù`, `|x| < 1`.

